{% set link = absolute_url(path('invite_user', { key, signature })) %}
<p>Hi there,</p>
<p>Someone on OpenHelp has invited you to join their workspace.</p>
<p>To set up your account and start collaborating, just click the button below:</p>
<p>
    <a href="{{ link }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
        Accept invitation
    </a>
</p>

<p>If the button doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<a href="{{ link }}">{{ link }}</a>

<p>If you weren’t expecting this invitation, feel free to ignore this email—no account will be created unless you complete the sign-up.</p>
